description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Beginner Elliptical Machine | Low Impact HIIT Workout' from the channel Fitscope.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Beginner Elliptical Machine | Low Impact HIIT Workout

In this beginner  level, low. impact, HIIT workout, Meghan takes you through intervals with increasing speed and resistance.  This class gives a great endurance and strength building workout, yet is still low impact so good for sensitive knees.

Soundtrack:  indie house 

Class Plan: 
2 min warmup 
17 min speed intervals 
1 min cool down

00:00 Warm up
01:52 Workout
19:40 Cool down
